//! # SIMD Vectorization Framework
//!
//! Platform-agnostic SIMD support with automatic vectorization:
//!
//! - **x86/x86_64**: SSE2 → SSE4.2 → AVX → AVX2 → AVX-512
//! - **ARM/AArch64**: NEON → SVE → SVE2
//! - **WebAssembly**: SIMD128
//!
//! ## Automatic Vectorization
//!
//! ```quanta
//! #[vectorize]
//! fn dot_product(a: &[f32], b: &[f32]) -> f32 {
//!     a.iter().zip(b).map(|(x, y)| x * y).sum()
//! }
//! ```
//!
//! ## Explicit SIMD
//!
//! ```quanta
//! use simd::v256::f32x8;
//!
//! fn vector_add(a: &[f32], b: &[f32], c: &mut [f32]) {
//!     for i in (0..a.len()).step_by(8) {
//!         let va = f32x8::load(&a[i..]);
//!         let vb = f32x8::load(&b[i..]);
//!         (va + vb).store(&mut c[i..]);
//!     }
//! }
//! ```

